title: Space Rangers - Episode 3 - The Replacements
description:
Episode 3 of 6.

The Replacements -The Rangers are assigned a new android troubleshooter, they dub "Ringer" (as in Dead), while they try to uncover the reasons behind a mining ship&#039;s hijacking. They&#039;re convinced that the ship is being used by a Hobbaba crime lord named Isogul for smuggling a deadly drug known as "Exjay", but if they cannot prove it, they have to return it. They also discover that Colonel Wiess plans to eventually replace all human Space Rangers with androids.

Please, keep seeding and look for the other episodes as well. Feel free to comment as well. Never before released on DVD. Science Fiction television series from the early 90&#039;s.
